| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3352 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2adfdc3a-a685-5c3a-864d-7b890ef52a0d"
